---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";

const lastUpdated = new Date("2026-06-18");
const dateLabel = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("en-US", {
  month: "long",
  day: "numeric",
  year: "numeric",
})
  .format(lastUpdated)
  .toUpperCase();
---

<Base title="Now" description="What Rafael Coelho is working on right now.">
  <div class="container-page">
    <header class="mb-12 pt-4">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">/ Now</p>
      <h1
        class="font-display mb-4 text-[2.4rem] font-medium tracking-tight"
        style="color: var(--color-text); letter-spacing: -0.025em;"
      >
        What I'm working on
      </h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase" style="color: var(--color-platinum-dim);">
        Last updated · {dateLabel}
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="hairline-gold mb-10" style="opacity: 0.35;"></div>

    <div class="prose-content">
      <h2>This week</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Shipping COELHO Nexus v1</strong> — Agentic RAG + GraphRAG search
          over YouTube transcripts. FastAPI + Qdrant + Neo4j + LangGraph on Oracle
          Free Tier.
        </li>
        <li>
          Wrapping up self-healing Playwright observability for the ingestion pipeline
          (Langfuse + OpenTelemetry).
        </li>
        <li>Migrating this site from Jekyll/al-folio to Astro 6 + Cloudflare Pages.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>This month</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Public launch of COELHO Nexus — first paying users in Brazil (Pix-first
          pricing), then LATAM and global tiers.
        </li>
        <li>
          Writing up the SOTA observability stack (Langfuse + OTEL + Grafana) we built
          for the Nexus pipeline.
        </li>
        <li>
          Talking to Senior AI/MLOps roles in the UAE (G42, Inception, Core42), Saudi
          Arabia, and Singapore.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Background</h2>
      <p>
        This is a
        <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"
          >/now page</a
        >. A regularly updated snapshot of what I'm focused on right now — not what
        I'd like to be doing, not a roadmap, not aspirational. Built for the person
        who already knows me and wants to know what to ask about.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
